## 10. 配置设计

建议使用 YAML 配置。

## 10.1 Provider 配置示例

```yaml
providers:
  - provider_id: docling_native_provider
    provider_type: docling
    name: Docling Native Provider
    access_mode: native_sdk
    enabled: true
    default_config:
      enable_ocr: false
      keep_page_meta: true

  - provider_id: docling_loader_provider
    provider_type: docling
    name: Docling Loader Provider
    access_mode: langchain_loader
    enabled: true
    default_config:
      export_type: doc_chunks
      keep_page_meta: true